about.summary: Provides several metrics for assessing relative importance in linear models. These can be printed, plotted and bootstrapped. The recommended metric is lmg, which provides a decomposition of the model explained variance into non-negative contributions. There is a version of this package available that additionally provides a new and also recommended metric called pmvd. If you are a non-US user, you can download this extended version from Ulrike Groempings web site.

name: r-relaimpo
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.2-5" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-relaimpo
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/relaimpo_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/relaimpo/relaimpo_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7fd12f6fac553b4cbb13688756bb94594a9e6db151fa389aaec6b816f359de6c

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-boot
    - r-corpcor
    - r-mitools
    - r-survey
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-boot
    - r-corpcor
    - r-mitools
    - r-survey

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('relaimpo')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('relaimpo')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://prof.beuth-hochschule.de/groemping/relaimpo/, http://prof.beuth-hochschule.de/groemping/
  license: GPL-2
  summary: Provides several metrics for assessing relative importance in linear models. These can be printed, plotted and bootstrapped. The recommended metric is lmg, which provides a decomposition of the model explained variance into non-negative contributions. There is a version of this package available that additionally
    provides a new and also recommended metric called pmvd. If you are a non-US user, you can download this extended version from Ulrike Groempings web site.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
